// An empty stub directory, so that the import still "resolves" from TS' POV.
// This was the home of Ember's preview types during the lead-up to publishing
// stable types from Ember's source code. If you have an import like this:
//
// ```ts
// import 'ember-source/types';
// import 'ember-source/types/preview';
// ```
//
// You can now remove the `preview` import:
//
// ```ts
// import 'ember-source/types';
// ```
